    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ACExrQiw6uip"
      },
      "source": [
        "In this cell we reorder train/validation/test proporthionaly for each folder  with photo for exthemle:\n",
        "-test\n",
        "--plant name\n",
        "---disease name"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "H8Zs7e9Kpwz3"
